bAutoLoadData:
Controls if the data referenced is automatically loaded.
If False then game code must call LoadData() on it's own.
DefaultImageResourceObject: The Default Image Resource, newly created CommonImage Widgets will use this style.
DefaultThrobberMaterial: The Default Throbber Material, newly created CommonLoadGuard Widget will use this style.
DefaultRichTextDataClass: The Default Data for rich text to show inline icon and others.
PlatformTraits: The set of traits defined per-platform (e.g., the default input mode, whether or not you can exit the application, etc...)
